snippet.title: PowerWash Simulator Back to the Future Special Pack Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Make dirt a thing of the past. The Back to the Future Special Pack for PowerWash Simulator is OUT NOW!

You can find PowerWash Sim and the Back to the Future Special Pack on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Nintendo Switch, Xbox Series S|X, Xbox One, Windows, and Steam. Plus, it is included with Xbox Game Pass! 

Find out more about PWS: https://powerwashsimulator.com/ 

Check out the Back to the Future Special Pack on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2464650/PowerWash_Simulator__Back_to_the_Future_Special_Pack/?curator_clanid=37637598
 

For more pressure washing goodness, subscribe to our channel!

Follow our Twitter for daily satisfying content: https://bit.ly/TwitterPWS

Join our Discord to join the conversation: https://discord.gg/powerwashsimulator

Follow us on TikTok for quick spray socials: https://bit.ly/PWSTikTok
